thread.title: Colin Anderson
thread.title_full: Omega Rental Cars reviewed by Colin Anderson

author: Colin Anderson
title: Colin Anderson
text:
We arrived at Queenstown airport from Australia and after calling Omega Rental Cars Frankton, were picked up, driven to office, paperwork done and in our new Toyota Corolla all within approx 30min. Fantastic! Returning the vehicle 9 days later, we received the same efficient, friendly service.
Would use again.
